body_html: OpKernels not loading when with Android is a common issue. It might have something to do with what's in this talk: https://youtu.be/0r9w3V923rk?t=19m39s. There's also a bunch of StackOverflow issues. Let us know if you're certain there's a bug in TensorFlow.
